    "詳情": "Marriage is incompatible. Illness requires careful medical consultation. Wealth must await the opportune moment. Caution is advised for Sericulture and Livestock. Residence Fortune is stagnant. Travellers are delayed. Pregnancy will result in a daughter. One must think thrice for all aspirations. Fung Shui is temporarily out of fortune. Await the time for lost items, do not ask further. No need for worry in the face of trouble for personal fortune. Weather/Timing is slightly disagreeable. Caution is advised, yet travel is not disadvantageous."
